{"tid":1379470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[7.28 警方濫暴．證據PO] 今晚衝突，警方濫暴場面眾多，材料已收集如下，隨便用","createTime":"2019-07-28T19:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T10:26:01.000Z","uid":54684,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2d47f5f22ce7d90cbed0a15ff9c60e9651e753c7","tid":1379470,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:40:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7.28 香港上環</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y15Cr4H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy15Cr4H.png&h=0ecce7b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴紅十字頭盔都打<br />\nPersonnels in red cross helmets were also beaten up. <br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377029/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oCZDbwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoCZDbwx.jpg&h=01085a16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n22:30 警方登上停車場狙擊樓下 <br />\nAt 22:30, policemen went up to a carpark building nearby to fire shots towards the protesters on the street below. <br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377765/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377765/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jwpzuiv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwpzuiv.png&h=ce7281c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小朋友亦被催淚煙傷到<br />\nEven children were attacked by the police using tear gas canisters. <br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377350/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377350/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LBgRwwZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLBgRwwZ.png&h=a617c06b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前線鋼板都射穿埋<br />\nLethal shots which can cause a hole on metal shields were fired by the police. <br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377493/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377493/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nZDbxk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nZDbxk.gif&h=a557dc67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑警對被捕者動私刑<br />\nA band of policemen was caught on camera when repeatedly abusing and attacking a man's head who was already subdued. <br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378018/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378018/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑警以燃燒彈攻擊記者<br />\nA policeman was caught on camera when throwing a firebomb to reporters nearby. <br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2979309865443391?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkon9agroup%2Fpermalink%2F2979309865443391%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyyy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=b7353e04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2979309865443391?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">隨便廣傳</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c9243f0dcdad9ca2a53f07ea9d85e7e084f6223a","tid":1379470,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:41:30.000Z","msg":"同場加映  好人好事<br />\n<br />\n示威者幫韓國旅客上頭盔保護佢地<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LostDutch/videos/2389701804613906/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLostDutch%2Fvideos%2F2389701804613906%2F&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyyy2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=6ac1b853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/LostDutch/videos/2389701804613906/</a>"},{"pid":"ea237f9a45dbbeb39dc0f2e178708c7155ef86c4","tid":1379470,"uid":54684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019